'''馬修·提摩西·霍普'''（{{lang-en|Matthew Timothy Hoppe}}；{{bd|2001年|3月13日}}）是一位[[美國|美國]]足球運動員，場上司职[[前鋒_(足球)|前锋]]，現在效力於[[西班牙足球甲級聯賽|西甲]]球隊[[皇家馬略卡體育會|皇家馬略卡]]，他也代表[[美國國家足球隊|美國國家足球隊]]參賽。

==球會生涯==
霍庇在[[亞利桑那州|亞利桑那州]]的巴塞罗那足球學院學習踢球，2019年6月與德國球會[[沙尔克04足球俱乐部|沙尔克04]]簽約加盟<ref>[https://www.onegoal.us/articles/2020/3/6/onegoal-interview-series-american-striker-talent-matthew-hoppe-on-his-move-to-schalke-04 OneGoal Interview Series: American Striker Talent Matthew Hoppe on his move to Schalke 04] {{Wayback|url=https://www.onegoal.us/articles/2020/3/6/onegoal-interview-series-american-striker-talent-matthew-hoppe-on-his-move-to-schalke-04 |date=20210112062732 }} onegoal.us</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://barcaresidencyacademyusa.com/barca-residency-academy-striker-matthew-hoppe-signs-with-fc-schalke-04/|title=Barça Residency Academy Striker Matthew Hoppe Signs with FC Schalke 04|website=Barca Residency Academy USA|date=2019-06-17|access-date=2021-01-10|archive-date=2020-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201210105056/https://barcaresidencyacademyusa.com/barca-residency-academy-striker-matthew-hoppe-signs-with-fc-schalke-04/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2020年11月28日，他首次代表球隊在德甲上場，對手是[[慕遜加柏體育會|慕遜加柏]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://schalke04.de/en/bundesliga-en/matthew-hoppe-everyone-helped-support-encourage/|title=Matthew Hoppe: Everyone helped to support and encourage me|website=FC Schalke 04|date=2020-11-29|access-date=2021-01-10|archive-date=2021-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111140849/https://schalke04.de/en/bundesliga-en/matthew-hoppe-everyone-helped-support-encourage/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2021年1月9日對[[賀芬咸1899體育會|賀芬咸]]，他打進個人首顆進球並戴帽，使球隊以4-0取勝。霍庇是首位美國球員在德甲戴帽，而他的入球亦終結了球隊接近一年，30場不勝的恥辱紀錄<ref>{{cite web|title=Schalke avoid Bundesliga longest winless run after Hoppe hat-trick|url=https://sports.yahoo.com/schalke-avoid-bundesliga-longest-winless-162915142.html|publisher=Yahoo Sports|date=2021-01-09|accessdate=2021-01-09|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128163538/https://sports.yahoo.com/schalke-avoid-bundesliga-longest-winless-162915142.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.espn.com/soccer/report?gameId=576675|title=Schalke's Hoppe nets hat-trick to snap 30-game winless run|website=ESPN|date=2021-01-09|accessdate=2021-01-09|archive-date=2021-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111125316/https://www.espn.com/soccer/report?gameId=576675|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=|first=|date=|title=Schalke recorded their first Bundesliga win in 31 games|url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/55602681|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210205143136/https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/55602681|archive-date=2021-02-05|access-date=2021-01-09|website=BBC|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==國家隊生涯==
2021年5月20日，對陣瑞士的友誼賽之前，霍普首次接到了[[美國國家足球隊|美國國家足球隊]]的徵召。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ussoccer.com/stories/2021/05/berhalter-calls-27-players-for-usmnt-camp-ahead-of-friendly-against-no-13-ranked-switzerland|title=BERHALTER CALLS 27 PLAYERS FOR USMNT TRAINING CAMP AHEAD OF FRIENDLY AGAINST NO. 13-RANKED SWITZERLAND|website=U.S. Soccer|date=2021-05-20|access-date=2021-07-27|archive-date=2022-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220116135531/https://www.ussoccer.com/stories/2021/05/berhalter-calls-27-players-for-usmnt-camp-ahead-of-friendly-against-no-13-ranked-switzerland|dead-url=no}}</ref>他入選了[[2021年美洲金盃|2021年美洲金盃]]的大名單。7月16日，霍普在第二場小組賽與法國海外大區[[馬提尼克足球代表隊|馬提尼克]]的比賽的中被提名為先發11人，這為他的國家隊首秀。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Goff |first1=Steven |title=In Gold Cup, former Virginia standout Daryl Dike scores twice as USMNT dominates Martinique |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/sports/2021/07/16/usmnt-martinique-gold-cup-daryl-dike/ |access-date=2021-07-27|work=The Washington Post |date=2021-07-16}}</ref>

2021年7月26日，霍普在1-0戰勝[[牙買加國家足球隊|牙買加]]的[[2021年美洲金盃|2021年美洲金盃]]八強賽中打進了他的第一個國家隊進球。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bundesliga.com/en/bundesliga/news/schalke-s-matthew-hoppe-scores-first-usmnt-goal-jamaica-2021-gold-cup-16665|title=Schalke's Matthew Hoppe scores first USMNT goal|website=Bundesliga|date=2021-07-26|accessdate=2021-07-27|archive-date=2021-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210818084045/https://www.bundesliga.com/en/bundesliga/news/schalke-s-matthew-hoppe-scores-first-usmnt-goal-jamaica-2021-gold-cup-16665|dead-url=no}}</ref>8月1日，他隨隊獲得[[2021年美洲金盃|2021年美洲金盃]]冠軍<ref name="冠軍">{{cite web|url=https://www.chinapress.com.my/20210802/%E2%97%A4%E7%BE%8E%E6%B4%B2%E9%87%91%E6%9D%AF%E2%97%A2-%E7%BD%97%E5%AE%BE%E9%80%8A%E5%8A%A0%E6%97%B6%E5%A4%B4%E7%90%83%E7%BB%9D%E6%9D%80-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%8A%E7%AC%AC7%E5%BA%A6/|title=◤美洲金杯◢ 罗宾逊加时头球绝杀 美国史上第7度夺冠|publisher=中國報|date=2021-08-02|access-date=2021-08-04|archive-date=2021-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210804203731/https://www.chinapress.com.my/20210802/%E2%97%A4%E7%BE%8E%E6%B4%B2%E9%87%91%E6%9D%AF%E2%97%A2-%E7%BD%97%E5%AE%BE%E9%80%8A%E5%8A%A0%E6%97%B6%E5%A4%B4%E7%90%83%E7%BB%9D%E6%9D%80-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%8A%E7%AC%AC7%E5%BA%A6/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

